---
---

<section class="bento-wrap" id="services" aria-labelledby="services-heading">
  <div class="bento-head">
    <div>
      <div class="kicker">What we do</div>
      <h2 id="services-heading" class="reveal">We do the tech bit.<br /><em>You run the business.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="reveal">Five things we are very good at. Most clients start with one and stay for the rest.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bento">

    <div class="tile tile-hero reveal" style="justify-content: space-between">
      <div class="orbit" aria-hidden="true" style="position: absolute;"></div>
      <span class="t-kick">The flagship</span>
      <div>
        <h3>AI agents. <em>They never call in sick.</em></h3>
        <p>Trained on your business. They answer calls at 2am, qualify leads, book appointments and follow up with every enquiry. Politely. Every time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tile tile-stat tile-glowstat reveal">
      <span class="big"><span data-count="30">0</span>+</span>
      <p>Hours a week the average small team loses to work a robot should be doing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tile tile-lav reveal">
      <span class="t-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <h3>Process audits</h3>
      <p>We map where hours and money quietly leak out of your business. Then we plug it. Permanently.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tile tile-vio reveal">
      <span class="t-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <h3>Custom apps</h3>
      <p>Portals, booking systems, dashboards. If you can describe it over coffee, we can build it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tile tile-soft reveal">
      <span class="t-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <h3>Integrations</h3>
      <p>Your CRM, calendar, inbox and invoicing. Finally talking to each other like adults.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tile tile-wide tile-stat tile-glowstat reveal">
      <span class="big"><span data-count="60">0</span>s</span>
      <p>How fast a new lead expects a reply before they call the next name on Google. Our agents respond instantly. Yours can too.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bento-wrap {
    padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) clamp(24px, 5vw, 72px) clamp(60px, 7vw, 100px);
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .kicker {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2.6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-purple-mid);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .kicker::before {
    content: '';
    width: 30px;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--color-purple-mid);
  }

  .bento-head {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .bento-head h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 5.4vw, 72px);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .bento-head h2 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--color-purple-mid);
  }

  .bento-head p {
    font-size: 16.5px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 34ch;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .bento {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    grid-auto-rows: minmax(210px, auto);
    perspective: 1400px;
  }

  .tile {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 34px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: 12px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #fff;
    transition: box-shadow 0.35s, border-color 0.35s;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    will-change: transform;
    --gx: 50%;
    --gy: 50%;
  }

  .tile::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: inherit;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: radial-gradient(420px circle at var(--gx) var(--gy), rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.13), transparent 65%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.35s;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .tile:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .tile > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .tile:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(107, 33, 168, 0.16);
    border-color: #C9B8E8;
  }

  .tile h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(21px, 1.9vw, 27px);
    letter-spacing: -0.4px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .tile p {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 36ch;
  }

  .tile .t-kick {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-purple-mid);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* Hero tile */
  .tile.tile-hero {
    grid-column: span 2;
    grid-row: span 2;
    background: var(--color-purple-deep);
    border-color: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .tile-hero h3 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 2.8vw, 40px);
    color: #fff;
    max-width: 14ch;
  }

  .tile-hero h3 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: #C4B5FD;
  }

  .tile-hero p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); max-width: 34ch; font-size: 15.5px; }
  .tile-hero .t-kick { color: #C4B5FD; }

  .orbit {
    position: absolute;
    top: -30%;
    right: -28%;
    width: 78%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 181, 253, 0.25);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .orbit::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 18%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 181, 253, 0.18);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .orbit::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: -4px;
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-purple-mid);
    box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.9);
  }

  .tile-hero:hover .orbit { animation: spin 14s linear infinite; }

  @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  /* Stat tile */
  .tile-stat { align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; }

  .tile-stat .big {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(54px, 5.5vw, 84px);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-purple-mid);
  }

  /* Colour variants */
  .tile-soft { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #F3EEFB, #E9DEFA); border-color: transparent; }
  .tile-lav { background: linear-gradient(150deg, #EDE4FA, #DCCBF6); border-color: transparent; }
  .tile-lav h3 { color: #4C1D95; }
  .tile-vio { background: linear-gradient(160deg, #7C3AED, #6021A8); border-color: transparent; color: #fff; }
  .tile-vio h3 { color: #fff; }
  .tile-vio p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75); }
  .tile-vio .t-line { background: #E9D5FF; }
  .tile-vio::before { background: radial-gradient(420px circle at var(--gx) var(--gy), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18), transparent 65%); }
  .tile-stat.tile-glowstat { background: linear-gradient(150deg, #FBFAFE, #F1EAFB); }
  .tile-hero::before { background: radial-gradient(480px circle at var(--gx) var(--gy), rgba(196, 181, 253, 0.22), transparent 65%); }
  .tile-wide { grid-column: span 2; }

  .tile .t-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 34px;
    left: 34px;
    width: 34px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-purple-mid);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .bento { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .tile.tile-hero { grid-column: span 2; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bento { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .tile.tile-hero { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; }
    .tile-wide { grid-column: span 1; }
  }
</style>
